  "title": "Account",
  "description": "<p><strong>Accountant – Scope of Work</strong></p>\n<p>1. Financial Record-Keeping</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Maintain full set of accounts (AP, AR, GL, bank reconciliation)</li>\n  <li>Record all income and expenses with proper documentation</li>\n  <li>Ensure accurate tracking of transactions by project or cost center</li>\n</ul>\n<p>2. Invoicing &amp; Payment</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Issue client invoices with correct GST breakdown</li>\n  <li>Monitor accounts receivable and follow up on overdue payments</li>\n  <li>Process vendor and subcontractor payments</li>\n  <li>Maintain monthly payment schedules and cash flow tracking</li>\n</ul>\n<p>3. Payroll &amp; CPF</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Calculate staff salaries and allowances</li>\n  <li>Process monthly payroll, including CPF and SDL contributions</li>\n  <li>Submit IRAS-related documents such as IR8A and Form IR21</li>\n</ul>\n<p>4. Financial Reporting</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Prepare monthly P&amp;L, Balance Sheet, and Cash Flow reports</li>\n  <li>Monitor job costing and monthly project performance</li>\n  <li>Assist with annual financial budgeting and forecasts</li>\n</ul>\n<p>5. Tax &amp; Compliance (including GST)</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Prepare and submit quarterly GST F5 returns</li>\n  <li>Maintain proper GST documentation for audit readiness</li>\n  <li>Ensure compliance with IRAS, ACRA, and MOM regulations</li>\n  <li>Coordinate with auditors for annual financial review</li>\n</ul>\n<p>6. Tender &amp; Project Support</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Provide financial data and costing for tenders</li>\n  <li>Track project costs, claims, and margins</li>\n</ul>\n<p>7. Admin &amp; General Support</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Manage petty cash and staff expense claims</li>\n  <li>Liaise with external accountants, corporate secretaries, and banks</li>\n  <li>Maintain proper filing of all finance-related records</li>\n</ul>",
