    "description": "<p>EAM Engineering Pte Ltd is a trusted and fast-growing contractor based in Singapore, specializing in electrical, plumbing, and renovation works for both residential and commercial units. We are BCA Registered, BizSafe Level 3 Certified, and an HDB Registered Contractor.<br>\n<br>\nOur clients include major brands like Go Pizza, Dairy Farm International, KJS Construction, and YHI Corporation, as well as facility management projects with top-tier companies such as McDonald’s Singapore (Hanbaobao Pte Ltd).<br>\n<br>\nAt EAM Engineering, we are committed to delivering:<br>\n\t•\tReliable and responsive service<br>\n\t•\tSkilled workmanship<br>\n\t•\tEfficient solutions for every project<br>\n<br>\nWe believe in building a strong internal team and providing a supportive work environment where employees can grow professionally while contributing to exciting and meaningful projects.<br>\n<br>\nOffice Location:<br>\n21 Woodlands Close, #09-19 Primz Bizhub, Singapore 737854<br>\nContact: 9114 2340 | Email: admin@eamengineering.com<br>\nWebsite: Coming soon!<br>\n</p>",
